            インデントでDOMの階層を表す。
            変数割り当てができたりする。

            ````
            doctype html
            html(lang="en")
              head
                title= pageTitle
                script(type='text/javascript').
                  if (foo) {
                     bar(1 + 5)
                  }
              body
                h1 Jade - node template engine
                #container.col
                  if youAreUsingJade
                    p You are amazing
                  else
                    p Get on it!
                  p.
                    Jade is a terse and simple
                    templating language with a
                    strong focus on performance
                    and powerful features.
            ````
